##########################################################################
 Creates simulated speckle data for a IDIMxIDIM array.
 From Jeff Morgan and Elliott (kiloho::jeff or kiloho::elliott)
 JLP95: add the possibility of no clipping
    (i.e. "continous frame", no Poisson clipping to simulate photon detection)

simu1.c
simu2.c  old version (1990)
simu3.c  new version (1995) JLP95: add the possibility of no clipping
    (i.e. "continous frame", no Poisson clipping which simulates 
     photon detection)

simu_mama.for
C To generate simulations of MAMA data
C Output: data file compatible with DECODE_MAMA, as generated by
C READ_MAMA
C Inside of a window 256x1024, object centered in (512,128).

